  "title": "Pungent Korean Farfalle Naengmyeon",
  "description": "A pungent and cheesy one-pot Korean dish featuring farfalle and naengmyeon, made with ayurvedic-sattvic-friendly ingredients. This en-croute style dish is perfect for a unique dinner experience.",
