      "name": "scallions",
      "amount": "1/4 cup",
      "notes": "chopped"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Heat sesame oil in a large pot over medium heat.",
    "Add gochujang and gochugaru, stir for 1 minute.",
    "Add naengmyeon noodles and cook according to package instructions.",
    "Add farfalle and cook until al dente.",
    "Stir in soy sauce and shredded vegan mozzarella until cheese is melted.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and top with additional mozzarella.",
    "Bake in a preheated oven at 375 degrees for 10 minutes.",
    "Garnish with chopped scallions and serve immediately."
